------------------------------------------------------
TSE includes
1) crawing module written by YAN Hongfei in Aug. 2003
2) indexing module by YAN Hongfei in Apr 2004
3) servicing module by YAN Hongfei in Apr 2004

	1) in tse.XXXXXX-XXXX.Linux.tar.gz
	2) and 3) in index.XXXXXX-XXXX.Linux.tar.gz

------------------------------------------------------

2. crawling module
1) unpack the software and compile it
tar xvfz tse.040422-1152.Linux.tar.gz
make

2) running
nohup ./Tse -c tse_seed.pku &

3) If you want repeat crawling,execute "sh Clean.sh"

note: all site in the "tse_unreachHost.list" will not be crawled

通过看文件名中包含的日期和时间获得最新的TSE包。e.g: tse.040422-1152.Linux.tar.gz 是目前(2004年4月22日11:52)最新的。
包解开后有README文件，仔细阅读，可能与以前的版本有些不同。

----------------------------------------------

hlink.080731-2355.tar.gz
	it is good for Red Hat Enterprise Linux AS release 3 (Taroon)
		and Ubuntu 8.04.1
	but files in "hlink" and "uri" dirs are older than those in tse.

